# CODEOWNERS — audience-router IA merge gate (ADR-034 §7 / Issue #1014)
#
# Files in the audience-segmented information architecture are subject to a
# 5-second-test merge gate. Changes to the home page, top-level navigation,
# audience route groups, and design tokens require review from a balanced
# pool of personas so the IA does not drift toward one audience over time.
#
# Reviewer pools — `@Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-retailer-personas` and
# `@Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-internal-personas` — are GitHub teams that
# must be created in the Azure-Samples org. Until the teams exist, GitHub
# falls back to the repository default reviewers; see
# `docs/governance/five-second-test.md` for the team-membership criteria
# and the activation runbook.

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Default — repository maintainers
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                                  @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-hub-maintainers

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Audience-router IA paths — 5-second-test merge gate
#  Both reviewer pools are required so home + nav are reviewed by personas
#  representing both retailer and internal audiences.
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Home page (audience-router)
apps/ui/app/page.tsx               @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-retailer-personas @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-internal-personas

# Top-level navigation / root layout
apps/ui/app/layout.tsx             @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-retailer-personas @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-internal-personas

# Retailer route group — retailer-persona reviewers required
apps/ui/app/(retailer)/**          @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-retailer-personas

# Builder route group — internal-persona reviewers required
apps/ui/app/(builder)/**           @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-internal-personas

# Deploy route group — both pools (the deploy lane is the funnel for both audiences)
apps/ui/app/(deploy)/**            @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-retailer-personas @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-internal-personas

# Shared shell & lane primitives (touch every audience)
apps/ui/components/shared/**       @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-retailer-personas @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-internal-personas

# Design tokens — both palettes must remain WCAG 2.2 AA
apps/ui/styles/tokens/**           @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-retailer-personas @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-internal-personas

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  ADRs — architecture team
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
docs/architecture/adrs/**          @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-hub-architecture
docs/architecture/ADRs.md          @Azure-Samples/holiday-peak-hub-architecture
